# libjxl optimization session вЂ” cumulative iter1+2+3 вЂ” 2026-04-27

Hardware: AMD Ryzen 9 7950X, 128 GB RAM (WSL2)
libjxl: github.com/libjxl/libjxl@HEAD + libjxl_combined_iter1_2_3.patch
Rust: this crate, default features (rayon + avx512), archmage runtime dispatch
Highway: x86-64-v2 baseline + AVX2/AVX3/AVX3_ZEN4 runtime dispatch

